TXmlTableParameter

    public abstract class TParseTreeNode
extends Object
implements Visitable, Iterator<TSourceToken>
    This class is the root class for all syntax/parse tree nodes. A syntax/parse tree node is composed of a sequence of tokens generated by the lexer.

    The syntax node usually includes sub-nodes such as a where clause including expression node.
    Check getNodeType() for type of this node.
    This node includes all tokens from start token and end token
